{"tid":2107991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"三星話6G快5G 50倍 5G巳out","createTime":"2020-07-14T08:43:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T09:15:47.000Z","uid":31907,"like":127,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"286623859119b9c1eb2aee018ef9de5790433cfc","tid":2107991,"uid":31907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T08:43:07.000Z","msg":"《韓聯社》報道，三星電子發布《下一代超連接體驗》白皮書，闡述6G願景，體現其加快技術研發搶佔市場領導地位的意願。<br />\n<br />\n白皮書提到，第六代流動通訊技術將達到T級(tera bps級)數據傳輸速率，無線網絡延遲小到微秒級。業界料2025年將啟動6G技術的標準化，2028年投入商用，2030年正式提供服務。<br />\n<br />\n白皮書並預測超實感擴展現實(Truly Immersive eXtended Reality)、高保真移動全息顯示(High-Fidelity Mobile Hologram)、數字複製(Digital Replica)等服務將問世。<br />\n<br />\n業界預計，6G的速度將達到5G的50倍，延遲縮短到5G的十分之一。6G時代開啟後，汽車、機械人、無人機、家電、顯示器等多種機械儀器將與互聯網連接。"},{"pid":"7085e7447147c05f3dc3cade0e02dfad71456c01","tid":2107991,"uid":194326,"like":146,"dislike":2,"score":144,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T08:44:26.000Z","msg":"三層又比兩層鬆化"},{"pid":"31e3ed26cb039d518e622b896782ffbf9dc2ff11","tid":2107991,"uid":38904,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T08:44:36.000Z","msg":"問題係點解決到發射站問題"},{"pid":"db9078bafec834d154822430a1ff887e8dd1b21b","tid":2107991,"uid":20170,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"7085e7447147c05f3dc3cade0e02dfad71456c01","tid":2107991,"uid":194326,"like":146,"dislike":2,"score":144,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T08:44:26.000Z","msg":"三層又比兩層鬆化"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T08:47:53.000Z","msg":"三十三？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bfce18a21386536261772bb30172bc410919482","tid":2107991,"uid":122275,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T08:47:55.000Z","msg":"如果真係28年整到咁整5G黎做乜春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b84e2d5351c7c0948ec1400c075598211321f29","tid":2107991,"uid":90328,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T08:48:31.000Z","msg":"5G都未用..."},{"pid":"290baa861e2ed6e0e