家電、顯示器等多種機械儀器將與互聯網連接。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T11:04:18.000Z","msg":"美帝推行緊啦喎"},{"pid":"92a394ef3d850cc0bb8fe8fc5599530ab918ba03","tid":2107991,"uid":78492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T11:05:56.000Z","msg":"不嬲十年一個G<br />\n又打曬飛機<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a87811454d982dce178fa341e3911106d84f38c8","tid":2107991,"uid":74927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T11:09:52.000Z","msg":"業界預計，6G的速度將達到5G的50倍，延遲縮短到5G的十分之一。<span class=\"red\">6G時代開啟後，汽車、機械人、無人機、家電、顯示器等多種機械儀器將與互聯網連接。</span><br />\n<br />\n5G個陣已經吹到咁啦 而家去到<br />\n6G都係一樣  7 8 9 10G 我諗都<br />\n見到同一句<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要而家5G都係<br />\n食左舊屎咁樣 仲講6G"},{"pid":"03ca12dcdbfdea1c397d0837219feddb1b0c1fc8","tid":2107991,"uid":317956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7aa36832d1298abd373d245c11467b389ab5c1ca","tid":2107991,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T10:12:19.000Z","msg":"一步一個發射站"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T11:10:32.000Z","msg":"其實唔一定，如果唔用二進制，有方法零一之外分多幾個數值，用低頻電磁波都可以增加內容量"},{"pid":"2ef1cb0b4bbd0b54acf91d4cb4f1b4b4fa45d21c","tid":2107991,"uid":195846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"39772d1379537a7709e71e142270857b9f7d6e54","tid":2107991,"uid":197852,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"29f12c487d70fc53fa3463f2f13bff501521d791","tid":2107991,"uid":25468,"like":10,"dislike":7,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T09:43:35.000Z","msg":"一分鐘就用晒啲data , 變番128k 地獄"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T10:05:56.000Z","msg":"速度同用糧都未識分？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T11:17:04.000Z","msg":"秒"},{"pid":"76c77e3de17fb0d24c728e9d09546fcdd394c382","tid":2107991,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"03ca12dcdbfdea1c397d0837219feddb1b0c1fc8","tid":2107991,"uid":317956,"like":0,"di